    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 7th level, you can move things with your mind with little effort. You can spend 5 chakra or use a bonus action to restore your use of hand signs, your willpower forcing them to move. Starting at 15th level, you ignore the hand sign component.</p><p>Also at 7th level, when you make a saving throw against an effect that would inflict a Mental or Sensory condition, you gain a 1d4 bonus to the result.</p>",
